    contents, blessed bags divide it by four, and cursed bags double
    it.

    Tipping or looking into a cursed bag of holding may make items
    vanish, with a separate 1/13 chance for each item.

    Some items should not be put in a bag of holding, or they will
    make the bag explode – scattering all of its contents, destroying
