spellbook of magic missile
	Allows you to learn the spell of magic missile.

	The magic missile ray does ((xplev/2) + 1)d6 damage + spell damage
	bonus, so higher-level spellcasters can deal significant damage
	with this spell. A level 30 character deals 16d6 damage with magic
	missile, averaging 56 damage per hit.

	This spell's damage is doubled for Knights by carrying the Magic
