	- If you zap yourself with a wand of slow monster, you will
	  become slow for 13-23 turns and abuse dexterity.

	Breaking:
	- Results in an explosion causing from 1 to (4 x charges) damage.
	  You and surrounding monsters are slowed.

	Engraving: Dust.
wand of noise
	When zapped, it emits a ray of sound.
	- Deals 6d6 damage to monsters in its path.
	- Sonic rays can bounce from walls and will destroy doors, iron
	  bars, and drawbridges.

	- Monsters hit by sonic rays are subject to sonic damage, which
	  can destroy glass and crystal items.
	- All potions are glass, so they are always vulnerable to breaking.
	  Rings, wands, and tools are all vulnerable to this damage if
