	Engraving: Dust.
	- The wand will issue some loud bands and wakeup nearby monsters.
wand of speed monster
	Zapping the wand at a monster gives the target(s) permanent
	intrinsic speed. Zapping the wand at yourself grants temporary
	intrinsic speed for 50-74 turns and also exercises dexterity.

	Monsters can zap the wand at themselves, and observing them doing
