	Engraving: Dust.
wand of striking
	Zapping this wand has the same effect as the force bolt spell
	- deals 2d12 damage to any monsters in its path
	- Destroys boulders, doors, statues, drawbridges, and fragile
	  items such as potions.
	- Its beam does not reflect

	Wands of striking have a fixed chance of hitting:
	- if the roll of a d20 is lower than (10 + monster's AC), the
