wand of undead turning
	A wand of undead turning has two functions:

	1) Zapping an undead monster deals 1d8 points of damage and will
	   cause the creature to flee from you. This damage is doubled if
	   you are a Knight carrying the Magic Mirror of Merlin.

	2) Alternatively, the wand can be used to unturn dead, reviving
