	- If you zap a water elemental, you will instead heal it for 6d6 HP.
	- If you zap an earth elemental, it turns into a mud elemental.

	- Amphibious and breathless monsters are not affected by water streams.
    - Monsters that like fire or lava (ex: fire vortex, lava demon)
